      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let this one go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it garage-kept and meticulously detailed. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or speck of dust on it. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
