    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Power is delivered via the legendary S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains impeccably rigid, with a reinforced rear subframe and a factory-spec limited-slip differential ensuring optimal torque distribution. Suspension geometry is true, utilizing aluminum control arms and fresh bushings for razor-sharp turn-in. This example is mechanically flawless, showing zero oil consumption and a pristine VANOS system, making it a definitive collector-grade specimen for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
