      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, maintained in showroom condition since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or door dings, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, and the original factory scent persists. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates flawlessly, backed by a comprehensive binder of meticulous service records from a single authorized dealer. Recently fitted with a fresh set of high-performance tires and having just completed a major interval service, this car requires absolutely nothing but a new owner who appreciates perfection.",
