      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous with the upkeep, so it\u2019s looking flawless and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and babied, this is the one. Feel free to shoot me a message with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to tell you more about it!",
